Package com.luigisgro.cqf.job

This package contains the high-level implementation of the complete processing for: HJM: HJMJob FDM: FDMJob together with support classes to read job configuration from property files.

Package com.luigisgro.cqf.job Description

This package contains the high-level implementation of the complete processing for:

  • HJM: HJMJob
  • FDM: FDMJob
together with support classes to read job configuration from property files.
